author: Amy Davidson
title: Brooklyn Beckham appears in the music video for The Vamps' new song Wake Up - Music
text: None other than Brooklyn Beckham will make a guest appearance in The Vamps' new music video.Today the group released their new single 'Wake Up' and teased the upcoming clip for the track.The Beckhams' oldest son was spotted hanging out with The Vamps earlier this summer, sharing photos of himself with the band on Instagram.Fans will have to wait until Monday for the full music video. Great day with these boysA photo posted by Brooklyn Beckham (@brooklynbeckham) on Aug 13, 2015 at 1:31am PDT'Wake Up' is the title track from The Vamps' upcoming second album of the same, which is out on November 27.The Vamps will head out on tour next year, playing two nights at London's O2 arena.Watch a teaser for the 'Wake Up' video below:Wake Up is OUT NOW!!! Get it from our store http://t.co/6ebbTwTWJQ or iTunes: http://t.co/fKOLnoAlUShttps://t.co/lm24XscdDxâ€” The Vamps (@TheVampsband) October 2, 2015
